headline: Franklin to Integrate Parts of Wamco, Cut Jobs Amid Outflows
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Franklin Resources Inc. will start taking over parts of its Western Asset Management Co. unit as the bond house grapples with a Securities and Exchange Commission investigation into its star bond manager, Ken Leech.
